sequenceDiagram
    participant Probe as OpenSlopCommandExecControlProbe
    participant Client as WorkbenchCore
    participant Daemon as core-daemon
    participant Provider as provider-domain
    participant Codex as codex app-server

    Probe->>Client: codex-command-exec-control-stream
    Client->>Daemon: start control stream
    Daemon->>Provider: stream command with control callback
    Provider->>Codex: command/exec(processId, streamStdoutStderr, streamStdin)
    Codex-->>Provider: outputDelta READY
    Provider-->>Daemon: outputDelta READY
    Daemon-->>Client: codex_command_exec_output_event READY
    Client-->>Daemon: codex-command-exec-write(PING\n)
    Daemon-->>Provider: write follow-up
    Provider->>Codex: command/exec/write
    Codex-->>Provider: outputDelta PING\n
    Provider-->>Daemon: outputDelta PING\n
    Daemon-->>Client: codex_command_exec_output_event PING\n
    Client-->>Daemon: codex-command-exec-terminate
    Daemon-->>Provider: terminate follow-up
    Provider->>Codex: command/exec/terminate
    Codex-->>Provider: final command/exec response
    Provider-->>Daemon: codex_command_exec_result
    Daemon-->>Client: codex_command_exec_result
